                    <span>To hear somebody else tell the story is one thing, to hear it from somebody who was there in the middle of it all, somebody who lived it--somebody like brilliant Andy Hertzfeld from the original Mac team is something else entirely.  Andy's deeply personal account of that "revolution" in that now famous valley is diamond sharp.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">For every Mac lover!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
